seo: Gateone,任意文件读取漏洞,CVE-2020-35736,漏洞检测
summary: 该插件用于检测Gateone应用是否存在CVE-2020-35736任意文件读取漏洞，通过构造特定请求检测是否能够成功读取系统文件。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the Gateone application has the CVE-2020-35736 arbitrary file read vulnerability by constructing specific requests to check if system files can be successfully read.
